OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPets must not replace      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchildren in Italy, warns   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FPope                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Starting a family in Italy is becoming 
OL,6, a "titanic effort" that only the rich  
OL,7, can afford, Pope Francis has warned.   
OL,9,FAddressing a conference on Italy's     
OL,10,Fdemographic crisis, he said pets were  
OL,11,Freplacing children in many households. 
OL,13,FAlso on stage were dozens of young     
OL,14,Fpeople, wearing t-shirts saying "we can
OL,15,Fdo this" - alluding to convincing      
OL,16,Fpeople to have more children.          
OL,18,FItaly has one of the lowest fertility  
OL,19,Frates in the EU and births dropped     
OL,20,Fbelow 400,000 last year - a new low.   
